# M6 — visualize the Heavy catwalk stuck bug.
#
# From bake trace: bot mid=2 (Heavy) starts at the RED spawn alcove (~288, 2072)
# and gets PERMANENTLY stuck at (540, 2054) for hundreds of ticks. Stuck=226+
# means the bot has been ~3 seconds without moving x by more than 0.5 px.
#
# Heavy chassis is the tallest. Spawn alcove has roof at row H-10 (=60).
# Just outside the alcove at tile x=15..30, there's a slope ramp that
# rises from y=2016 (96 px above floor) up to cw1_top=1280. The Heavy
# walks out of the alcove and gets stuck against either the slope's
# leftmost vertex or its underside.

window 1280 720
seed 1 0
out build/shots/m6_bot_catwalk_stuck
map catwalk
loadout heavy "Auto-Cannon" Sidearm Light Standard
spawn_at 288 2072

# Hold RIGHT to walk toward (and past) the slope
at 5   shot stand_t005
at 30  press right
at 60  shot walk_t060
at 90  shot walk_t090
at 120 shot stuck_t120
at 180 shot stuck_t180
at 240 shot stuck_t240
at 300 shot stuck_t300

# Try jumping to escape
at 240 press jump
at 245 release jump
at 280 press jet
at 320 release jet
at 360 shot post_recover_t360

contact_sheet stuck_sheet cols 4

at 400 end
